        Common constructor for the RelationAwareSet.
        Parameters:
        owner - The DomainObject that owns this collection
        relation - The relation of which this set is a part of
        mapKey - The function that returns the key used to index this collection.
        internalMap - The backing collection for this side of the relation. If this is null, then the internalMapGetter will be used when the collection is needed.
        internalMapGetter - The function that returns the internalMap when it is needed. Can be null if it is never needed.
